"{\"uid\": \"punchng.com-man-arrested-for-climbing-eiffel-tower-on-final-olympics-day\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Most Widely Read Newspaper  The Olympic rings are being installed on the Eiffel Tower for the upcoming Paris 2024 Olympic Games, in Paris on early June 7, 2024.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 160, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 132, \"end\": 137, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999481588, \"rank\": 5.192291255417868e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Photo by Sameer Al-Doumy / AFP)  Kindly share this story:  Aman was arrested for climbing the Eiffel Tower on Sunday, hours before the Olympics closing ceremony, Paris police told the BBC.The man was spotted climbing the tower at about 14:45 local time (13:45 BST) and officers immediately intervened and arrested him, police said.\", \"from\": 161, \"to\": 493, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 171, \"end\": 177, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sameer_Anjaan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0040951899187405e-19, \"text\": \"Sameer\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sameer_Anjaan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sameer_Anjaan\"}, {\"begin\": 189, \"end\": 192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9999999910642146, \"rank\": 8.935773812046558e-09, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}, {\"begin\": 221, \"end\": 225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valinor\", \"score\": 0.9306935714948036, \"rank\": 0.06708918563141952, \"text\": \"Aman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valinor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vali